sources.description: Dvd ISO copy of all 18 discs of the Shirley Temple Little Darling Collection: Baby Take A Bow (1934) (B&W/Color) The Blue Bird (1940) (Color) Bright Eyes (1934)Â  (B&W/Color) Captain January (1936) (B&W/Color) Curly Top (1935) (B&W/Color) Dimples (1936) (B&W/Color) Heidi (1937) (B&W/Color) Just Around The Corner (1938) (B&W/Color) The Little Colonel (1935) (B&W/Color) Little Miss Broadway (1938) (B&W/Color) The Little Princess (1939) (Color) The Littlest Rebel (1935) (B&W/Color) Rebecca Of Sunnybrook Farm (1938) (B&W/Color) Stand Up And Cheer (1934) (B&W) Stowaway (1936) (B&W) Susannah of the Mountains (1939) (B&W/Color) Wee Willie Winkie* (1937) Young People (1940) (B&W) *2 separate ISO, one B&W one Sepia Ripped with AnyFox, ISO created with ImgBurn MKV files ripped from discs using MakeMKV, uncompressed hence the large file size
